  "prompt": "Where can I found a large range of formal and evening wear in Gold Coast?",
  "response": "In Gold Coast, there are several places where you can find a large range of formal and evening wear. Here are some options to consider:\n\n1. **Pacific Fair Shopping Centre** - This is one of the largest shopping centers in the Gold Coast, featuring a variety of stores that offer formal and evening wear, including both local and international brands.\n\n2. **Robina Town Centre** - Another major shopping destination with a range of fashion retailers that specialize in formal and evening attire.\n\n3. **Broadbeach** - This area has several boutiques that focus on formalwear. Check out local shops and designers who may offer unique pieces.\n\n4. **Formalwear Specialty Stores** - Look for stores specifically dedicated to formal and evening wear. Some popular options in the Gold Coast include:\n   - **A Formal Affair**\n   - **Tiffany's Formal Wear**\n   - **The Formal Suit Company**\n\n5. **Online Options** - If you prefer shopping online, many retailers offer delivery to Gold Coast. Websites like The Iconic or ASOS have extensive formal wear selections.\n\n6. **Local Boutiques** - Explore smaller boutiques in areas like Surfers Paradise or Burleigh Heads for unique options and personalized service.\n\n7. **Rental Services** - If you're looking to rent rather than buy, consider services like **Dress for a Night** or **The Volte**, which offer a range of designer formal and evening wear.\n\nBefore heading out, it's a good idea to check the store's website or call ahead to ensure they have the styles and sizes you need.",
